Class I18N

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.eckhartarnold.client.I18N

  • public class I18N
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains an instance of class I18NConstans with the translations of all string constants that GWTPhotoAlbum uses.

    Presently internationalization does not work due because language detection of the client is still missing. (Any volunteers?)
